_json.description: Pistachio and Almond Tart with Orange and Cardamom    Source: adapted from Casa Moro, by Sam and Sam Clark  Note: Since shelling your own pistachios is a real pain (literally!), try to find them pre-shelled - Indian, Turkish, Persian and Middle Eastern shops (or shops that sell things imported from these countries) are good places to look.
